com.mesosphere.sdk.framework

Class FrameworkScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mesosphere.sdk.framework.FrameworkScheduler

  • public class FrameworkScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
    Implementation of Mesos' Scheduler interface. There should only be one of these per Scheduler process. Received messages are forwarded to the provided MesosEventClient instance.
